title: Marine Botany Laboratory
description: One laboratory weekly and several field trips. Focuses on marine algae, fungi, and angiosperms.

pre_req_data.text: Prerequisite(s): BIOL 20A, BIOE 20B, and BIOE 20C, and satisfaction of the Entry Level Writing and Composition requirements. Must be taken concurrently with BIOE 120.

class_notes: Concurrent enrollment in BIOE 120 is required.
